## 📂 Project Structure

```
resumechecker/
├── client/                     # React Frontend (Vite)
│   └── src/
│       ├── api/axios.js        # Axios instance with auth headers
│       ├── components/         # Navbar, Sidebar, ProtectedRoute
│       ├── context/            # AuthContext (JWT state management)
│       ├── layouts/            # DashboardLayout
│       └── pages/              # Login, Register, DashboardHome,
│                               # ResumeUpload, ATSAnalysis, JobMatches
└── server/                     # Express Backend
    ├── config/                 # DB connection config
    ├── controllers/            # User, Resume, Job, Analyze controllers
    ├── middleware/              # Auth, Error, Rate Limit, Upload, Validation, Metrics
    ├── models/                 # User, Job (Mongoose schemas)
    ├── routes/                 # User, Resume, Job, Analyze routes
    ├── services/               # 7 service modules (parsing, ATS, matching,
    │                           # industry template/readiness, job fetch, analyze)
    ├── utils/                  # JWT token generator
    └── seeder.js               # Sample job data seeder
```
